data.description: Wait NO longer!!  ASSUMABLE FHA @ 2.5% INTEREST RATE**  📌 SAVE OVER $1K PER MONTH in your monthly payment   📍 SAVE OVER $400,000 OVERALL in interest!!  What are you waiting for?!? Make this YOUR HOME TODAY!!  This lovely home features the 'Gambrill View Overlook floorplan'. The open floor plan allows you to take it ALL in the MOMENT that you open the door!!   ***This 3yr young End Unit Townhome is READY for you to call it yours!! No more WAITING for new construction!! This is as close to new build as you're going to find!  Be in before the LEAVES drop off the trees in Autumn!!  Amenities include 7” wide luxury plank vinyl floors, a 12ft kitchen island/breakfast bar with granite countertops, soft close shaker cabinetry & stainless appliances in the kitchen. Plenty of space for all of your kitchen and cleaning wares in the spacious pantry.   The powder room on the first floor is perfect for hosting.   Recessed LED disk lighting on 1st floor and on stairs.   The open stairs continues the theme of the open floor plan throughout the entire home.   Boasting 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms.  You'll be amazed at the size of the owner's suite! The EnSuite will comfortably fit a 6 piece King Size bedroom set with ample space to have you feeling like you're sleeping in the lap of luxury.  The beautiful EnSuite and it's luxury 7' Spa Shower features dual rainfall showerheads. There are also double sinks and separate water closet (toilet) to make getting ready a breeze. There is also a spacious closet featuring lots of space for your entire wardrobe.   The 2nd full bath on the 2nd level also have double sinks & tub/shower for those days where you're all getting ready simultaneously. The large linen closet in this full bath is perfect for all of your linen.    Both of your 7' Spa Showers feature ceramic tile shower floors!  Ceramic tile floors in all bathrooms!  Ceramic tile shower walls in all bathrooms!    The laundry room with Smart Washer & Dryer on the 2nd floor makes doing laundry a breeze. No more lugging laundry up and down the stairs.   Let's continue the journey to the LOFT on the top level!  This is where the fun continues! The entire carpeted, top level is open.. use your imagination.. you choose how you'd like to use this living space.. LOFT living, studio style.. family room, office, WFH or entertainment?!?   If it's not enough to have the first Luxury 7' Spa Shower.. the full bath on the top level also features a luxury 7' Spa Shower with a rainfall showerhead, double sinks and linen closet.   The spaciously, exquisite 3rd floor terrace offers a spanning scenic view of the Mountains of Gambrill State Park!! You'll enjoy spending serene evenings on your  tranquil terrace!   So much more for you to take in when you tour this  alluring home.   Custom LEVELOR ® blinds throughout the entire home.   3-panel interior doors with brushed nickel hardware.  1x4 side and 1x6 top square door casing.  1x4 square edge base moulding.   Open wire shelving in pantry, laundry and all closets (linen included).   The spacious detached 2 car garage provides covered off street parking and plenty of space for additional storage!   **Neighborhood features**  Community of 199 homes   Easy access to commuter routes (Routes 155, 70, 40 and 270).  Community Pool, 24 hour fitness center, 2.5 miles to Historic Downtown.
